    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "Description of the pupa, female and male genitalia of Aedes (Howardina) guerrero Berlin and first record of Ae. (How.) guatemala Berlin (Diptera: Culicidae) in Puebla, Mexico" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151086>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151074>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151072>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151078>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151080>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151076>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151082> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151086>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Female of Aedes (Howardina) guatemala. a) Foretarsus; b) midleg; c) hindleg. Fe-II, midfemur; Fe-III, hindfemur; Ta-I, foretarsomere; Ta-II, midtarsomere; Ta-III, hindtarsomere; Ti-II, midtibia; Ti-III, hindtibia; subscripts 1–3, individual tarsomeres." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10151086/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151074>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Female of Aedes (Howardina) guerrero. a) Foreleg; b) midleg; c) hindleg. Fe-II, midfemur; Ta-I, foretarsomere; Ta- II, midtarsomere; Ta-III, hindtarsomere; Ti-I, foretibia; Ti-II, midtibia; Ti-III, hindtibia; subscripts 1–5, individual tarsomeres." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10151074/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151072>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Female of Aedes (Howardina) guerrero. a) Head and thorax, dorsal view; b) lateral view of habitus showing the thoracic pleura. Ds, Dorsocentral stripes, Fe-II, midfemur; Mks, mesokatepisternum; Ppn, postpronotum; Sc, scutum; V, vertex." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10151072/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151078>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Male genitalia of Aedes (Howardina) guerrero. a) Dorsal view; b) gonostylus. Ae, aedeagus; Cl, claspette; Gc, gonocoxite; GC, gonostylar claw; Gs, gonostylus; Ppr, paraproct; IX-Te, tergum IX; IX-TS, setae of tergum IX; IX-TL, tergum IX lobe." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10151078/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151080>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Male genitalia of Aedes (Howardina) guerrero. a) Tergum IX; b) proctiger; c) tergum IX, aedeagus and proctiger. Ae, aedeagus; CSe, cercal setae; Par, paramere; Ppr, paraproct; PprT, paraproct teeth; IX-TS, setae of tergum IX; IX-TL, tergum IX lobe." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10151080/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151076>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Female genitalia of Aedes (Howardina) guerrero. a) Tergum VIII; b) sternum VIII; c) genitalia, ventral view; d) terminal abdominal segments,lateral view.Ce, cercus; I, insula; LVL, lower vaginal lip; PGL, postgenital lobe; SCa, spermathecal capsule; UVL, upper vaginal lip; VIII-Te, tergum VIII; IX-Te, tergum IX; 1–5-S, setae of sternum VIII." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10151076/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151082>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Pupa of Aedes (Howardina) guerrero. a) Cephalothorax; b) metanotum and abdomen. CT, cephalothorax; GL, genital lobe; Pa, paddle; I–IX, abdominal segments I–IX; 0–14, setal numbers for specified areas." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10151082/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

